item.title: CVE-2023-6814|2024-06-28T01:57:04.242Z -- hitachi -- cosminexus%20component%20container
item.description: Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File vulnerability in Hitachi Cosminexus Component Container allows local users to gain sensitive information.This issue affects Cosminexus Component Container: from 11-30 before 11-30-05, from 11-20 before 11-20-07, from 11-10 before 11-10-10, from 11-00 before 11-00-12, All versions of V8 and V9.
